Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with resource management in small cell networks.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper formulates a dynamic stochastic game between small cell base stations.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper proposes a control policy for optimizing energy efficiency.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper considers the optimization of bits per unit power.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve multimedia traffic in the small cell network.
